{
  "id": "69f6902c280d2b1d47054062",
  "title": "遠くの自然より近くの自然",
  "created": 1777766447,
  "updated": 1777791748,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69f6902c280d2b1d47054062",
      "text": "遠くの自然より近くの自然",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766447,
      "updated": 1777766856
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902d000000000014aaf0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766447,
      "updated": 1777766447
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf1",
      "text": "from 2026/05/03 [vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766460
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf2",
      "text": " 過ごしてる部屋の窓から自然が見えてほしい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766448
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6921d000000000014ab17",
      "text": "  アパートの部屋の窓があまり素敵でなかったからそう思った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766943,
      "updated": 1777766996
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69294000000000014ab1b",
      "text": "   空や緑がない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767062,
      "updated": 1777767065
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6921d000000000014ab16",
      "text": "   大自然の北海道にある賃貸物件の緑のない窓だった",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766942,
      "updated": 1777767025
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69270000000000014ab19",
      "text": "   5m先に隣家の窓と壁が見えた",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767025,
      "updated": 1777771792
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69275000000000014ab1a",
      "text": "   実家の窓(牧草地の平原が見える窓)に比べると素敵でない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767030,
      "updated": 1777767050
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69224000000000014ab18",
      "text": "   この部屋で[一番気に入ってるのは…値段だ]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766949,
      "updated": 1777767099
    },
    {
      "id": "69f692ad000000000014ab1c",
      "text": "   都会的で良いとも思う",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767086,
      "updated": 1777777244
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf3",
      "text": "  物件の謳い文句で「車で15分走れば大自然にアクセスできる」などがあるけど、普段の生活では見えなさそう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777767182
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6930e000000000014ab1f",
      "text": "   私個人にとって得点でなかっただけで、誰かにとって良さそうな点があれば何でも知らせてくれる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767183,
      "updated": 1777767252
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf4",
      "text": "  千本ぐらいの桜並木の場所に行かなくても、",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766448
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf5",
      "text": "   (でもこの体験はこれでしか得られない)",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766448
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf6",
      "text": "  部屋の窓から見えるところに桜が咲いてたり、散歩道や移動経路にちょこちょこあれば幸せ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766448
    },
    {
      "id": "69f690ee000000000014ab07",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766640,
      "updated": 1777766640
    },
    {
      "id": "69f690ee000000000014ab08",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766640,
      "updated": 1777766640
    },
    {
      "id": "69f690f5000000000014ab09",
      "text": "部屋で過ごす時間が少ないなら豊かな窓は必要ない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766646,
      "updated": 1777767306
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6937a000000000014ab20",
      "text": " 窓に求める生活への貢献が少ない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767291,
      "updated": 1777767309
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf8",
      "text": " 外で過ごす時間が長いならあまり見ない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766661
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69102000000000014ab0a",
      "text": " 寝て起きるだけなら質素な窓で大丈夫",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766659,
      "updated": 1777766693
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aaf9",
      "text": " 長く部屋で過ごす人が豊かな窓を選べばいい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777767320
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69140000000000014ab0d",
      "text": " すべての部屋に豊かな窓があったほうがいいということはない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766721,
      "updated": 1777767325
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6939c000000000014ab21",
      "text": "  最近、すべての部屋に豊かな窓があればいいのにと思ってた [vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767325,
      "updated": 1777767340
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6908d000000000014ab04",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766543,
      "updated": 1777766543
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6908d000000000014ab05",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766543,
      "updated": 1777766543
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aafa",
      "text": "贅沢な悩みだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766545
    },
    {
      "id": "69f690d6000000000014ab06",
      "text": " 実家の窓が良すぎる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766616,
      "updated": 1777766619
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aafb",
      "text": "  実家はその立地から窓の向こうの景色が豊か",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766738
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69150000000000014ab0e",
      "text": "  同じ地域の家でも窓の向こうが隣家の窓になる部屋はたくさんある",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766738,
      "updated": 1777766742
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69042000000000014aafe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766467,
      "updated": 1777766467
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aafc",
      "text": "タワーマンションの窓から空しか見えないとき、これも自然がないといえそう？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766467
    },
    {
      "id": "69f693be000000000014ab22",
      "text": " どうやったら自然を増やせるんだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767359,
      "updated": 1777767363
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6902e000000000014aafd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766448,
      "updated": 1777766469
    },
    {
      "id": "69f693c8000000000014ab25",
      "text": "観葉植物や[フェイクグリーン]を置けばいい",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767370,
      "updated": 1777767374
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69045000000000014aaff",
      "text": "身近に自然を置きたいなら窓の外よりも、部屋の中に置くほうが貢献度が高そう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766470,
      "updated": 1777767413
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69176000000000014ab0f",
      "text": " 部屋にいるとき、窓の外にはあまり注目しない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766775,
      "updated": 1777766813
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6917f000000000014ab11",
      "text": " 部屋の中の緑は何をしていても視界に入る",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766784,
      "updated": 1777766805
    },
    {
      "id": "69f693d2000000000014ab26",
      "text": " 窓の問題ではなかったのかも",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777767379,
      "updated": 1777767392
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6906d000000000014ab02",
      "text": " 試しに置いてみよう[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766510,
      "updated": 1777767399
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6eec00000000000755746",
      "text": " 　[シノクラッスラ]を用意した",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777790657,
      "updated": 1777790678
    },
    {
      "id": "69f691a3000000000014ab12",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777766820,
      "updated": 1777766820
    },
    {
      "id": "69f695d600000000006719b0",
      "text": "[窓から見える自然が強い][mtane0412.icon]",
      "userId": "6923e3b6e09f0be0924872ef",
      "created": 1777767894,
      "updated": 1777775718
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6958200000000006719ab",
      "text": "> [@mtane0412 https://twitter.com/mtane0412/status/1703199673086063017]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777767810,
      "updated": 1777767862
    },
    {
      "id": "69f695b500000000006719ad",
      "text": "> … ",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777767862,
      "updated": 1777767862
    },
    {
      "id": "69f695b500000000006719ae",
      "text": "> [https://gyazo.com/6384c4c6da8a3c6b3b842c3b4c8e28dc]",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777767862,
      "updated": 1777767862
    },
    {
      "id": "69f695b500000000006719af",
      "text": " 大自然すぎる問題w[inajob.icon][Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "65e1289acd012200235729c0",
      "created": 1777767862,
      "updated": 1777791748
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6ef6e0000000000effaff",
      "text": "  うちの実家は梅雨時期に部屋にナメクジが入ってきたりして、その自然はいらない！となってた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1777790831,
      "updated": 1777790863
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6958200000000006719ac",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ae7fecf7766b7001455cbd3",
      "created": 1777767810,
      "updated": 1777767810
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69cec0000000000539ace",
      "text": " 大根をしばらく放置していたら葉っぱが伸びて花が咲いてしまったので、デスクの周りにおいて自然を楽しもうかな[atohs.icon]",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777769708,
      "updated": 1777769748
    },
    {
      "id": "69f69ced0000000000539acf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5a61856392ee03001413cde3",
      "created": 1777769709,
      "updated": 1777769709
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6ed7a000000000075573d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777790331,
      "updated": 1777790331
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6ed7a000000000075573e",
      "text": "↔ 近くの自然より遠くの自然[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777790331,
      "updated": 1777790615
    },
    {
      "id": "69f6ed800000000000755740",
      "text": "　部屋には山やグランドキャニオンが入らないので",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1777790337,
      "updated": 1777790625
    }
  ]
}